# yabai -m rule --add app="^Karabiner-EventViewer$"   scratchpad=karabiner2   grid=12:12:6:1:5:5


# defaul spaces for apps
yabai -m rule --add app="^TypingClub$"              space=s_primary
yabai -m rule --add app="^OBS Studio$"              space=s_primary

yabai -m rule --add app="^Windows\ App$"            space=s_development
yabai -m rule --add app="^Screen\ Sharing$"         space=s_development
